Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.91,0:02:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有1分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有30秒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,7 6 5...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.15,0:03:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.18,0:03:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基德一定会趁这阵光亮混进来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.16,0:03:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要掉以轻心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.46,0:03:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警…警官 太阳眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你小子…是基德吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.53,0:04:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 用合成树脂做成的脸部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摸上去就和真的一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.67,0:04:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基德
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.64,0:04:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就先告辞了 拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.72,0:04:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站住 基德
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.91,0:04:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基德
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快追
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐电梯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.07,0:04:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.71,0:05:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开车
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.79,0:05:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
